{
  "texts": [
    "Sensitivity analysis of α.",
    "In our experiments, we focus solely on tuning the value of α, while adopting all other hyperparameters directly from prior work.",
    "To evaluate its impact, we present a sensitivity analysis of α in Figure 4.",
    "The results indicate consistent performance improvements for smaller α values, such as 0.1 and 0.25, but a decline as α increases, ultimately resulting in degeneration as α approaches ∞.",
    "These findings underscore the importance of balancing sequence-level and token-level rewards, with sequence-level rewards playing a more significant role, as evidenced by the small optimal α values."
  ]
}